   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Greetings to Papontos. I, Ptolemaios, salute you. Just as those to whom I was recommended by my brother Diogenes at that time showed me all good will and respect, [l. 5] so too now you, when you have been asked, will want to show me equal good will [l. 10] and respect . . . private wine of Paulos . . . [verso] [hand 2] from Ptolemaios, steward . . .</ab>
